  { src: "/future-in-bloom/1.jpg", alt: "Future In Bloom" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="Future In Bloom Pt. I"
  date="October 18, 2025"
  location="Belgium"
  type="Coworking"
  description="Embodied AI coworking and build sessions pushing practical robotics work forward."
  images={images}
>
  <p>Future In Bloom is our coworking format - no talks, no structure, just builders in a room working on embodied AI projects together. The first edition focused on practical robotics: training models, debugging hardware, and sharing what works.</p>
  <p>The kind of session where someone across the table solves a problem you've been stuck on for a week, and you return the favor an hour later.</p>
</EventLayout>
